Alexander Asro https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexander_Asro 0 Alexander Asro (also: Aleksander Azro; February 10, 1888 – January 1963) was a film and theatre actor. He was a member of the Vilna Troupe and appeared in several comedic films in the United States.
